      <title>Hazeltree 报告称，空头押注航空公司和银行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/shortsellers-bet-against-airlines-banks-hazeltree-report-says-2024-09-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据和科技公司 Hazeltree 周三发布的报告显示，8 月份空头将目光瞄准了航空股，因为人们对受盈利下滑和价格上涨困扰的航空业的悲观情绪日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/shortsellers-bet-against-airlines-banks-hazeltree-report-says-2024-09-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
